  <brief_title>IV Sildenafil Persistent Pulmonary Hypertension Of The Newborn</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label Single Arm, Single Centre Study to Investigate the Safety and Efficacy of IV Sildenafil in Neonates With Persistent Pulmonary Hypertension of the Newborn (PPHN)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
