  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the efficacy of iv sildenafil in term and near term infants with PPHN
      (persistent pulmonary hypertension of the newborn), by measuring the need for inhaled nitric
      oxide (iNO) or extracorporeal membrane oxygenation (ECMO) compared to a historical control
      group not treated with sildenafil.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
