  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Babies &lt; 72 hours old and at least 34 gestational weeks with PPHN or hypoxic
             respiratory failure associated with idiopathic PPHN, meconium aspiration, sepsis or
             pneumonia

          -  Oxygenation index &gt;15 and &lt; 60

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Congenital anomaly

          -  Large left to right intracardiac or ductal shunt

          -  Already on inhaled nitric oxide
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
